OL,3,CMuriel McKay's son to come face-to-
OL,4,Cface with mother's killer in bid to
OL,5,Cfind body
OL,7,FThe son of a woman kidnapped and
OL,8,Fpresumed murdered in a case of
OL,9,Fmistaken identity more than half a
OL,10,Fcentury ago is travelling to Trinidad
OL,11,Fto meet the man convicted of killing
OL,12,Fher as the family attempts to find her
OL,13,Fbody.
OL,15,FMuriel McKay was taken in 1969 after
OL,16,Fcriminals wrongly thought she was
OL,17,Fmedia mogul Rupert Murdoch's then-
OL,18,Fwife, and planned to demand a #1m
OL,19,Fransom.
