OL,3,CMuriel McKay's son to come face-to-
OL,4,Cface with mother's killer in bid to
OL,5,Cfind body
OL,7,FShe was actually the wife of Mr
OL,8,FMurdoch's deputy Alick McKay. Two men
OL,9,Fwere jailed for murder but Ms McKay's
OL,10,Fbody has never been found.
OL,12,FOne of her killers, Nizamodeen Hosein,
OL,13,Fwho has been deported from the UK,
OL,14,Fbroke his silence telling Muriel's
OL,15,Ffamily she is buried at Stocking Farm
OL,16,Fin Hertfordshire.
OL,18,FSeveral searches were carried by
OL,19,Fpolice earlier this year and in 2022
OL,20,Fbut nothing was found.
