OL,3,CMuriel McKay's son to come face-to-
OL,4,Cface with mother's killer in bid to
OL,5,Cfind body
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News London Muriel's
OL,8,Fson Ian McKay hoped his trip to see
OL,9,FHosein would help bring him back to
OL,10,Fthe UK so he could show police where
OL,11,Fshe is buried.
OL,13,FNizamodeen, the kidnapper, is not
OL,14,Flooking as fit as he might do," Ian
OL,15,Ftold ITV News.
