OL,3,CMuriel McKay's son to come face-to-
OL,4,Cface with mother's killer in bid to
OL,5,Cfind body
OL,7,F"We do need to bring him to the UK, he
OL,8,Fmight pass on, and therefore we need
OL,9,Fto get as much information as we can
OL,10,Fpossibly get from him and possibly
OL,11,Fthings that he may be concealing," Ian
OL,12,Fexplained.
OL,14,FBoth the police and other members of
OL,15,FMuriel's family have already visited
OL,16,FHosein in Trinidad, but he has now
OL,17,Fasked to meet with her son.
OL,19,FIan said: "I'm really going to do a
OL,20,Fjob in this particular situation and
OL,21,Fthat's the only way I can look at it.
