OL,7,FAsked why Nizamodeen had not been
OL,8,Fbrought to the UK to help with the
OL,9,Fsearch, Met Police said in a statement
OL,10,Fearlier this year: "Our view has
OL,11,Falways been that we do not believe it
OL,12,Fwould provide us with beneficial
OL,13,Finformation and therefore we would not
OL,14,Fformally approach the Home Office who
OL,15,Fwould be required to grant permission.
