OL,3,CMuriel McKay's son to come face-to-
OL,4,Cface with mother's killer in bid to
OL,5,Cfind body
OL,7,F"We carefully reviewed this decision
OL,8,Fduring the search and, based on
OL,9,FHosein's reliability as a witness and
OL,10,Fthe likelihood of a successful
OL,11,Foutcome, we stand by our original
OL,12,Fdecision.
OL,14,F"As we have said previously, Muriel's
OL,15,Ffamily are aware it would not be
OL,16,Fproportionate to carry out any further
OL,17,Fsearches and that our investigation is
OL,18,Fnow at an end. We are saddened that we
OL,19,Fwere unable to bring them the closure
OL,20,Fthey so desperately long for."
